ZH: 他的身高一年比一年增长。
EN: His height has been increasing year by year.

ZH: 近年来，这个城市的人口增长迅速。
EN: In recent years, the population of this city has grown rapidly.

ZH: 这种植物在适当的条件下会快速增长。
EN: This plant will grow rapidly under the right conditions.

ZH: 公司的利润在过去一年里有所增长。
EN: The company's profits have increased in the past year.

ZH: 中国的经济增长速度令人惊讶。
EN: The speed of China's economic growth is astonishing.

ZH: 这家餐厅的生意在周末时增长最快。
EN: This restaurant's business grows the fastest on weekends.

ZH: 他们预计明年的销售额将继续增长。
EN: They expect sales to continue to increase next year.

ZH: 这个国家的农业产量已经增长了20%。
EN: The agricultural output of this country has increased by 20%.

ZH: 近几个月来，他的信心明显增长了。
EN: His confidence has obviously grown over the past few months.

ZH: 环境恶化导致疾病的增长。
EN: The deterioration of the environment leads to the increase of diseases.

ZH: 这个村庄的人口在过去十年里增长了50%。
EN: The population of this village has grown by 50% in the past ten years.

